Check Status Health is Reporting Correctly
    [Arguments]    ${healthStatus}

    ${healthStatus} =   Get From Dictionary  ${SERVICE_HEALTH_STATUSES}  ${healthStatus}

    Wait Until Keyword Succeeds
    ...  40 secs
